title: Avey Tare & Kria Brekkan - Pullhair Rubeye (3 versions)
description:
Avey Tare (of Animal Collective) and his wife, Kria Brekkan's album "Pullhair Rubeye."  The album was released from Paw Track Records in April 2007.  

Track listing includes the origional version, a reverse version of every song and tracks 3, 6, and 7 played back in double speed.

1. Sis Around the Sandmill
2. Opis Helpus
3. Foetus No-Man
4. Who Wellsus in my Hoff
5. Lay Lay Off, Faselam
6. Palenka
7. Sasong
8. Was Onaip
